<title>USA: Grancare, Living Centers name CEO.</title>
<headline>Grancare, Living Centers name CEO.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-07-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Apollo Management LP, Living Centers of America Inc and GranCare Inc on Monday named Keith Pitts as chairman and chief executive officer of the new company to be formed in the recapitalization and merger of Living Centers and GranCare.</p>
<p>The combined entity will be a large provider of long-term care services, with pro forma revenues of about $1.9 billion. Apollo will own 45 percent of the new company's stock.</p>
<p>Pitts, 40, is a former executive vice president and chief financial officer of OrNda HealthCorp and is a director of several public and private health care services companies.</p>
